00:36:45,828 --> 00:36:49,081
Sepertinya ada drama hubungan inses.

627
00:36:49,165 --> 00:36:51,709
Kita bisa tampil di Anderson Cooper
akhir pekan ini.

628
00:36:51,792 --> 00:36:53,419
Ya, pasti.

