00:42:25,167 --> 00:42:26,210
Sayang sekali.

682
00:42:27,795 --> 00:42:29,213
Karena kau sudah mati.

683
00:42:30,673 --> 00:42:34,009
Kematian menimpa kita semua, Edith.

684
00:42:36,220 --> 00:42:40,307
